]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<img width="524" height="350" src="http://nairobinews.nation.co.ke/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/2607coupleflirting.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="PHOTO | FILE" style="float:left; margin:0 15px 15px 0;" srcset="http://nairobinews.nation.co.ke/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/2607coupleflirting-300x200.jpg 300w, http://nairobinews.nation.co.ke/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/2607coupleflirting.jpg 524w" sizes="(max-width: 524px) 100vw, 524px" /><p>Members of popular Facebook group <em>Kilimani First Wives</em>¬†poured out their hearts at the prospects of their husbands ignoring them and taking mistresses for dates on Valentine‚Äôs Day.</p>
<p>The wives were discussing how mpango wa kandos should keep off as their men would be busy the whole day.</p>
<p>Some wives were however sure their men would ignore them this Valentine&#8217;s in preference to mistresses.</p>
<p>The debate eventually turned to who, between the wife and mistress, deserves a treat during Valentine‚Äôs Day.</p>
<p>Here are some of the sentiments shared on the group.</p>
<p>‚ÄúToday not the best day to take your mpango wa kando (mwk) for a date. Very risky. First wives wako keen today like no other day,‚Äù one wife wrote.</p>
<p>‚ÄúKama kuna mtu nangoja wangu asahau niko na yeye leo in fact atanikuta kwa gate ya job na mngoja leo kamutu ameumia,‚Äù another added.</p>
<p><strong>CHANGE OF DIET</strong></p>
<p>‚ÄúCalm your titties and go to work. Mzee atakuja tu. Change of diet is good, you should try it too,‚Äù one retorted.</p>
<p>‚ÄúThe fact remains that your man is a cheat. If he can leave you and go take mwk out on Val&#8217;s day, it means wewe hauko. Mwk is special whether being used or not,‚Äù another commented.</p>
<p>‚ÄúMwenye atapelekwa out leo ndiye special so watch your space and know your position,‚Äù another advised.</p>
<p>‚ÄúYaani am here stressed up coz wangu amechukua off we spend the day together and I had my own plans and you are there complaining of who is special than the other,‚Äù another wondered.</p>
<p>‚ÄúLearn to love yourself more and such nonsense will never bother you,‚Äù one wrote.</p>
