<p>She also captained the team for three years before handing the reins to current skipper Mercy Moim.</p>
<p>She will be remembered for her outspoken nature, and specifically for the outburst with the Kenya Volleyball Federation officials in 2015, which led to her temporary exclusion from the team.</p>
