<p>Justice Luka Kimaru on Thursday dismissed Miguna&#8217;s deportation as null and void and that it had no merit in law.</p>
<p>Justice Kimaru further directed the Immigration Department to deposit Miguna&#8217;s revoked passport to the registrar of court within seven days.</p>
<p>In his ruling, the Judge reasoned that Miguna was deported at a time Inspector General of Police Joseph Boinnet and Director of Criminal Investigation George Kinoti were in contempt of court orders.</p>
